You just arrived at IARC and you want to access the cluster ?

1. First, request your access by sending an email to IT-Services@iarc.who.int
2. Check the documentation here : https://readthedocs.sit.iarc.fr/index.html 
3. Access the cluster here : https://portal.sit.iarc.fr/pun/sys/dashboard
4. You want to run a job interactively ? Just click on one of the apps (RStudio, JupyterLab, Visual Studio Code...) 
5. You want to run a job using the shell ? Just go in Clusters and Osiris Shell Access

